Interface OwlsAssignInputClient

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OwlsAssignClient
All Known Implementing Classes:
OwlsAssignInputClientImpl
public interface OwlsAssignInputClient
extends OwlsAssignClient

A representation of the model object 'Assign Input Client'.

The following features are supported:

  • Client Reference
  • Input References
  • Outputs References
